<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Formular</head><p>Formular eines Vidimus des Abtes Mauritius von St. Egidien zu Nürnberg auf Bitten des Rats der Stadt Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_546" id="272v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="head"><ab facs="#facs_546_r2l12"><expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> <expan>vıdim<ex>us</ex></expan> vom Abbt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l13">cʒu ſant Egıdien etc </ab>
</div>
<div type="content"><pb facs="#facs_546"/>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l14">VVir Mauricıus Abbt des Cloſters der Schotten cʒu ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l15">Egıdien cʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> ſant Benedıcten <expan>orde<ex>n</ex>s</expan> in Bamberg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l16">Bẏſtum gelegen / Bekennen vnd tun kunt <expan>offenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l17">diſem brief / daʒ vvir einen gancʒen guten gerechten <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſigelte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l18">brief <expan>geſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geleſen vnd verhört <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / der von vvort </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l19">cʒu worte <expan>abgeſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt vnd lautet als <expan>hernachgeſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſtet </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l20">ſtet <expan>L<ex>i</ex>t<ex>tera</ex></expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l21">Vnd des cʒu <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>obg<ex>enanter</ex></expan> Mauricius Abbt von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l22">bete vvegen der Erſamen vveẏſen ~ der <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des Rats </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l23">der Stat cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> dicʒ <expan>vıdim<ex>us</ex></expan> vnd abſchrift mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_546_r2l24">Abbteẏ <expan>anhangend<ex>en</ex></expan> Jnſıgell 
<add><ab facs="#facs_546_line_1592997534035_199"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>igelt</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . am . etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_546" id="272v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="head">
<ab><expan>For<ex>ma</ex></expan>
<expan>vidim<ex>us</ex></expan> vom abbt czu sant Egidien etc. </ab>
</div>
<div type="content">
<ab><pb facs="#facs_546"/>Wir, Mauricius, abbt des closters
                                                der schotten czu sant Egidien czu
                                                  <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g,</expan> sant Benedicten
                                                  <expan>orde<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, in Bamberg bystum
                                                gelegen, bekennen und tun kunt
                                                  <expan>offenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit disem
                                                brief, daz wir einen ganczen, guten, gerechten
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelte<ex>n</ex></expan> brief
                                                  <expan>geseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, gelesen und
                                                verhört <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> der von wort
                                                czu worte <expan>abgeschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist,
                                                und lautet als
                                                  <expan>hernachgeschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> stet.
                                                  <app>
<note><q type="inline"><expan>L<ex>i</ex>t<ex>tera</ex></expan>.</q>Der Ausdruck dient hier als Platzhalter für
                                                  den zu vidimierenden Urkundentext.</note>
</app>Und des czu <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> so
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir,
                                                  <expan>obg<ex>enanter</ex></expan> Mauricius,
                                                abbt, von bete wegen der ersamen, weysen, der
                                                  <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des rats der stat
                                                czu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, dicz
                                                  <expan>vidim<ex>us</ex></expan> und abschrift mit
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> abbtey
                                                  <expan>anhangend<ex>en</ex></expan> insigell
                                                  <add><expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>igelt</ex></expan></add>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> am etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
